<p>35<br/>my lot to meet. I feel very much for his home folk.</p>
<p>The bombardment lately has been very severe, the large guns make this place rattle again.</p>
<p>I have been for some great rides lately in the Car. Saw Reg White the other night it was like old times yarning with him. I get on well with the folk here sat up until 11 o'c last night trying to pick up a little French. The girl is charming What! by name Jeanne. We have great fun getting grass for the rabbits of an evening.</p>
